Description: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character.  Enhances the accuracy of a power by {Boost.Attrib.Accuracy.Scale}% and damage by {Boost.Attrib.Damage.Scale}% and reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.Recharge.Scale}% .    This enhancement can only be slotted by Corruptors and may be slotted into any Corruptor damage power.
DisplayName: Superior Attuned Superior Scourging Blast C
